Melissa Claire Egan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Melissa_Claire_Egan 0 Melissa Claire Egan (born September 28, 1981) is an American actress, best known for her roles as Annie Lavery on All My Children and Chelsea Lawson on The Young and the Restless.
